### ============================================
### Custom Properties - APIs REST
### ============================================
###
### Gestiona custom properties de tu organización
### para agrupar y clasificar repositorios.
### ============================================

### Variables de configuración
@token = {{$dotenv GITHUB_TOKEN}}
@org = {{$dotenv GITHUB_ORG}}
@baseUrl = https://api.github.com
@apiVersion = 2022-11-28

### =========================================
### 📋 PASO 1: Consultar el esquema existente
### =========================================

### Listar todos los custom properties definidos en la org
GET {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{org}}/properties/schema
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### =========================================
### 🏗️ PASO 2: Crear custom properties
### =========================================

### Crear o actualizar custom properties en la org
### Este ejemplo crea 3 properties: environment, team y criticality
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{org}}/properties/schema
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "properties": [
    {
      "property_name": "environment",
      "value_type": "single_select",
      "required": false,
      "description": "Entorno del servicio",
      "allowed_values": [
        "production",
        "staging",
        "development"
      ],
      "values_editable_by": "org_and_repo_actors"
    },
    {
      "property_name": "team",
      "value_type": "single_select",
      "required": false,
      "description": "Equipo responsable del repositorio",
      "allowed_values": [
        "backend",
        "frontend",
        "platform",
        "security",
        "data"
      ],
      "values_editable_by": "org_and_repo_actors"
    },
    {
      "property_name": "criticality",
      "value_type": "single_select",
      "required": false,
      "description": "Nivel de criticidad del repositorio",
      "allowed_values": [
        "high",
        "medium",
        "low"
      ],
      "values_editable_by": "org_and_repo_actors"
    }
  ]
}

### =========================================
### 🏷️ PASO 3: Asignar valores a repos
### =========================================

### Asignar custom properties a repos específicos (en lote)
### Modifica los nombres de los repos según tu organización
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{org}}/properties/values
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repository_names": [
    "repo-api-backend",
    "repo-payments-service"
  ],
  "properties": [
    {
      "property_name": "environment",
      "value": "production"
    },
    {
      "property_name": "team",
      "value": "backend"
    },
    {
      "property_name": "criticality",
      "value": "high"
    }
  ]
}

### Asignar properties a un segundo grupo de repos
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{org}}/properties/values
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repository_names": [
    "repo-webapp-frontend",
    "repo-admin-dashboard"
  ],
  "properties": [
    {
      "property_name": "environment",
      "value": "production"
    },
    {
      "property_name": "team",
      "value": "frontend"
    },
    {
      "property_name": "criticality",
      "value": "medium"
    }
  ]
}

### =========================================
### 🔍 PASO 4: Consultar custom properties
### =========================================

### Listar TODOS los repos de la org con sus custom properties
GET {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{org}}/properties/values?per_page=30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### Filtrar repos por un custom property específico
### Ejemplo: obtener solo repos con environment=production
GET {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{org}}/properties/values?repository_query=props.environment:production
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### Filtrar por múltiples properties
### Ejemplo: repos de producción del equipo backend
GET {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{org}}/properties/values?repository_query=props.environment:production props.team:backend
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### =========================================
### 📦 PASO 5: Consultar properties de un repo
### =========================================

### Obtener los custom properties de un repo específico
@repo = nombre-del-repo
GET {{baseUrl}}/repos/{{org}}/{{repo}}/properties/values
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}
